{% comment %}
Set up checkbox for enabling content blocks, options for positioning content blocks, and instructions for positioning content blocks in settings_schema.json.  Here is an example for featured collections:

 {
    "type": "checkbox",
    "id": "featured_collections_enabled",
    "label": "Featured Collections Enabled",
    "default": true
 },
 {
    "type": "select",
    "id": "featured_collections_pos",
    "label": "Position",
    "options": [
        { "value": "2", "label": "2" },
        { "value": "3", "label": "3" },
        { "value": "4", "label": "4" },
        { "value": "5", "label": "5"}
    ],
    "default": "2"
 },
{
    "type": "paragraph",
    "content": "Select the position in which you want the Featured Collections to appear on the Homepage (Position 1 is reserved for the Homepage Slideshow)"
},
{
    "type": "paragraph",
    "content": "NOTE: make sure each of your Homepage sections have different positions, or else they may not display!"
}

{% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
Assign a variable as an array of position numbers in index.liquid
{% endcomment %}
{% assign hp_sections = '2,3,4,5' %}

{% comment %}
Then split the array into individual items after each comma
{% endcomment %}
{% assign hp_sections = hp_sections | split: ',' %}

{% comment %}
Write a for loop.  Write if / elsif statements inside that for loop for each section (check it's position then check to see if it's enabled in the settings)
{% endcomment %}
    {% for i in hp_sections %}
          {% if settings.featured_collections_pos == i and settings.featured_collections_enabled %}
              {% comment %}
              some code for that section
              {% endcomment %}
          {% elsif settings.featured_links_pos == i and settings.featured_links_enabled %}
              {% comment %}
              some code for that section
              {% endcomment %}
          {% elsif settings.blog_pos == i and settings.blog_enabled %}
              {% comment %}
              some code for that section
              {% endcomment %}
          {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}